            <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Only have a single project running on <a href="http://www.redmine.org/">redmine</a>? want
it to be the homepage?</p>

<p>In <code>config/routes.rb in cofig/routes.rb</code></p>

<pre><code data-language="ruby">map.home '', :controller =&amp;gt; 'projects', :action =&amp;gt; 'show', :id =&amp;gt; 'my_project_name'
</code></pre>
